WEBVTT

00:00:02.433 --> 00:00:03.033
Charles.

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.500
You trained all day?

00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:05.133
No wonder

00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:06.466
you've won 24 times!

00:00:08.233 --> 00:00:09.700
Take one pill twice a day.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:10.500
Don't forget.

00:00:12.866 --> 00:00:13.700
God...

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:15.300
I didn't take one this morning.

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:20.966
Vitamins?

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.000
Give me some.

00:00:22.133 --> 00:00:23.066
Go buy your own.

00:00:23.666 --> 00:00:24.633
I'll just take two.

00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:27.800
Since when are you so petty?

00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:45.866
Charles...

00:00:46.066 --> 00:00:46.933
Are you okay?

00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.800
Get some rest tonight!

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:52.533
Tomorrow is

00:00:52.533 --> 00:00:53.800
the press conference.

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:12.600
What's going on?

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:14.700
What medicine is that?

00:01:14.700 --> 00:01:16.100
Why am I so hot now...

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:26.900
Damn!

00:01:27.500 --> 00:01:28.600
Why isn't it working?

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:36.000
Hello?

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:36.966
Joseph.

00:01:37.150 --> 00:01:37.700
What meds

00:01:37.700 --> 00:01:38.833
did you give me?

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:39.500
Why do I

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:40.766
feel like I got drugged...

00:01:41.300 --> 00:01:42.500
How many did you take?

00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:43.933
Just two pills.

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:46.033
I'm on my way.

